Author: fruitluvr22
Text: Thank you for sharing this because I feel the same way. I convince myself to eat instead of fast some days and I plan my meals down so anally and once everything is put together and I take the first couple bites, I'm just pretty bummed. It's been keeping the binges at bay but I can't help but feel guilty for wasting my calories right after. Yet, I do the same thing the following day. I think I'm brain dead
